## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="8b3c7-177">以程式設計方式使用物件模型 (Object Model) 發出工作流程執行個體時，這個屬性只能在設計階段使用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8b3c7-177">This property is used only at design time, while programmatically emitting a workflow instance using the object model.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8b3c7-178">它代表參考尚未編譯之事件處理常式的 XAML。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8b3c7-178">It represents XAML that references the event handler, which has not been compiled yet.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8b3c7-179">這個屬性包含 `Hashtable`，具有事件名稱和事件處理常式名稱/值組。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8b3c7-179">This property contains a `Hashtable`, with event name and event handler name-value pairs.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8b3c7-180">編譯後，此事件屬性就會直接與處理常式產生關聯。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8b3c7-180">After compilation, the event property is associated directly with the handler.</span></span>  
  
 [!INCLUDE[DependencyPropertyRemark](~/includes/dependencypropertyremark-md.md)]  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="8b3c7-181">下列範例顯示如何設定 <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Serialization.WorkflowMarkupSerializer.EventsProperty> 相依性屬性的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8b3c7-181">The following example shows how to set the value of the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Serialization.WorkflowMarkupSerializer.EventsProperty> dependency property.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
CodeActivity code1 = new CodeActivity();  
Hashtable eventsHashtable = new Hashtable();  
eventsHashtable.Add("ExecuteCode", "methodName1");  
code1.SetValue(WorkflowMarkupSerializer.EventsProperty, eventsHashtable);  
```
